Woman, verily, O Gautama, is a sacrificial fire. In this case the sexual organ
is the fuel; when one invites, the smoke; the vulva, the flame; when one
inserts, the coals; the sexual pleasure, the sparks.

In this fire the gods offer semen. From this oblation arises a person (purusa).
